  <name>The Prime Meridian</name>
  <intro />
  <introformat>1</introformat>
  <content>&lt;p&gt;Greenwich Mean Time (GMT) is centered on the Prime Meridian at the Royal Observatory in Greenwich, London.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="text-align:center; animation:pulse 2s infinite;"&gt;&lt;div style="width:10px; height:100px; background:red; margin:auto;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="color:red; font-weight:bold;"&gt;0° Longitude&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;style&gt;@keyframes pulse { 0% { opacity:1; } 50% { opacity:0.3; } 100% { opacity:1; } }&lt;/style&gt;</content>
